How to Force Tomcat to Use Your Log4j.xml
-----------------------------------------

Suppose your webapp's have local log4j.xml files but you want to increase or adjust the logging

Solution:  Modify setenv.bat/setenv.sh
--------------------------------------
  a) Modify the setenv.bat
       set JAVA_OPTS=-Dlogback.configurationFile=/path/to/logback.xml"
   
   b) Create a c:\tools\logging\log4j.xml
   
   
